external_knowledge:
UniProt entries represent unique identifiers for protein sequences and their functional information; 
 Gene expression values quantify the activity of a gene in a given context;
 Having at least one associated UniProt entry implies that a gene has known functions or interactions documented in the UniProt database.

sql:
SELECT user_id, access_duration
FROM access_logs
WHERE access_duration > (SELECT AVG(access_duration) FROM access_logs);
